lead_paragraph: The first wave of an expected 70,000 England fans descended on Marseille on Thursday and wasted no time establishing a foothold in Vieux Port to start three days of drinking and singing ahead of Saturday's Euro 2016 match against Russia.

headline.print_headline: England in Marseille Sparks Memories of Soccer's Dark Days
